-Common English words (the, and, is)
-Non-game-code words

Keep:
-[planet_class_xxx]
-$VARIABLE$
-Â§Y, Â§!, Â§R (color codes)
-Â£energyÂ£, Â£mineralsÂ£ (icon codes)

3. Translate with AI Correctly
Recommended prompt:
